high_descs: Go straight, then left into the hallway, then left again into the room with the white diningtable.
Pick up the spatula from the table.
Exit the room the way you came in and take the first left to the bathroom.
Place the spatula on the rim of the kitchen sink.
Go back to the diningtable in the earlier room.
Pick up the other spatula.
Go back to the earlier sink.
Place the second spatula on the rim of the kitchen sink.
anns.task_desc: Place two spatulas on the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Turn left to enter the passage and walk down the passage to reach the white diningtable.
Pick up the spatula from the table.
Turn around and walk to the bathroom on the left.
Put the spatula on top of the sink.
Turn around and walk left to reach the diningtable.
Pick up the spatula from the table.
Turn around and walk to the bathroom on the left.
Put the spatula on top of the sink next to the other spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put two Spatulas on the Sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the spatula from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the spatula into the sink.
Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the spatula from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Put the spatula on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Collect the spatula on the sink.
